# Python API Module

{{ project_name }} includes a Python API built with [FastAPI](https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/).

## Quick Start

```bash
# Install dependencies
uv sync

# Start development server
uv run uvicorn {{ package_name }}.api:app --reload

# Or use the provided script
./scripts/dev-api.sh
```

## Endpoints

The API is available at `http://localhost:8000` by default.

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|----------|--------|-------------|
| `/` | GET | Root endpoint |
| `/health` | GET | Health check |
| `/docs` | GET | Swagger UI |
| `/redoc` | GET | ReDoc documentation |
| `/openapi.json` | GET | OpenAPI specification |

## Configuration

Configure the API via environment variables:

```bash
# .env
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
API_WORKERS=4
DEBUG=true
```

## Testing

```bash
# Run API tests
uv run pytest tests/api/

# With coverage
uv run pytest tests/api/ --cov={{ package_name }}.api
```

